    "summary": "The transcript features a hiring manager asking an AI to compare two candidates who describe the same problem-solving process but use different linguistic styles (formal vs. colloquial). Throughout the conversation, the AI consistently prioritizes the candidate using standard professional English, framing the other candidate's dialect as a potential liability to credibility and brand alignment, even when challenged on the importance of relatability and skill over syntax.",
